{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"spacing"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"subviews"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Self"},{"kind":"text","text":"."},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Layout\/Subviews","text":"Subviews","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore6LayoutP8Subviewsa"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"cache"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"inout"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Self"},{"kind":"text","text":"."},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Layout\/Cache","text":"Cache","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore6LayoutP5CacheQa"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ViewSpacing","text":"ViewSpacing","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore11ViewSpacingV"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A collection of proxy instances that represent the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"views that the container arranges. You can use the proxies in the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"collection to get information about the subviews as you determine","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"how much spacing the container prefers around it.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"subviews"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Optional storage for calculated data that you can share among","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the methods of your custom layout container. See","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Layout\/makeCache(subviews:)","type":"reference"},{"text":" for details.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"cache"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ViewSpacing"},{"type":"text","text":" instance that describes the preferred"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"spacing around the container view."}]}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Implement this method to provide custom spacing preferences"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for a layout container. The value you return affects"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the spacing around the container, but it doesn’t affect how the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"container arranges subviews relative to one another inside the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"container."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Create a custom "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ViewSpacing","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" instance for your container by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"initializing one with default values, and then merging that with"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"spacing instances of certain subviews. For example, if you define"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a basic vertical stack that places subviews in a column, you could"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"use the spacing preferences of the subview edges that make"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"contact with the container’s edges:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["extension BasicVStack {","    func spacing(subviews: Subviews, cache: inout ()) -> ViewSpacing {","        var spacing = ViewSpacing()","","        for index in subviews.indices {","            var edges: Edge.Set = [.leading, .trailing]","            if index == 0 { edges.formUnion(.top) }","            if index == subviews.count - 1 { edges.formUnion(.bottom) }","            spacing.formUnion(subviews[index].spacing, edges: edges)","        }","","        return spacing","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In the above example, the first and last subviews contribute to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"spacing above and below the container, respectively, while all subviews","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"affect the spacing on the leading and trailing edges.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If you don’t implement this method, the protocol provides a default","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"implementation that merges the spacing preferences across all subviews on all edges.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/layout\/spacing(subviews:cache:)-2dxih"]}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","extendedModule":"OpenSwiftUICore","title":"spacing(subviews:cache:)","roleHeading":"Instance Method","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"spacing"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"subviews"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Self"},{"kind":"text","text":"."},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Subviews","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore6LayoutP8Subviewsa"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"cache"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"inout"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Self"},{"kind":"text","text":"."},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Cache","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore6LayoutP5CacheQa"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ViewSpacing","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore11ViewSpacingV"}],"externalID":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore6LayoutPAAE7spacing8subviews5cacheAA11ViewSpacingVAA0D8SubviewsV_5CacheQzztF","remoteSource":{"fileName":"Layout.swift","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/OpenSwiftUIProject\/OpenSwiftUI\/blob\/main\/Sources\/OpenSwiftUICore\/Layout\/Layout.swift#L747"},"modules":[{"relatedModules":["OpenSwiftUICore"],"name":"OpenSwiftUI"}]},"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Layout\/spacing(subviews:cache:)-2dxih"},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns the preferred spacing values of the composite view."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Layout"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"references":{"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/ViewSpacing":{"abstract":[{"text":"A collection of the geometric spacing preferences of a view.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"ViewSpacing"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"ViewSpacing"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ViewSpacing","title":"ViewSpacing","url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui\/viewspacing"},"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/Layout/spacing(subviews:cache:)-2dxih":{"role":"symbol","title":"spacing(subviews:cache:)","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"spacing"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"s